Description: Extends the archived 'SelvarMix' 1.2.1 implementation for
             regularized variable selection in model-based clustering.
             Variables are ranked with penalized mixture models
             and assigned clustering, regression, redundant, or independent
             roles. Missing values can be handled with a parsimonious
             class-only MNARz mechanism using either a decoupled SRUW workflow
             or an explicit joint SRUW-MNARz workflow.
